    Class and Description
    bt.torrent.fileselector.SelectionResult

  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    bt.module.ProtocolModule.contributeExtendedMessageHandler(Binder)
    since 1.5 in favor of ProtocolModuleExtender.addExtendedMessageHandler(String, Class) and its' overloaded versions
    bt.module.ProtocolModule.contributeHandshakeHandler(Binder)
    since 1.5 in favor of ProtocolModuleExtender.addHandshakeHandler(Class) and its' overloaded versions
    bt.module.ProtocolModule.contributeMessageHandler(Binder)
    since 1.5 in favor of ProtocolModuleExtender.addMessageHandler(int, Class) and its' overloaded versions
    bt.module.ServiceModule.contributeMessagingAgent(Binder)
    since 1.5 in favor of ServiceModuleExtender.addMessagingAgentType(Class) and ServiceModuleExtender.addMessagingAgent(Object)
    bt.module.ServiceModule.contributePeerSourceFactory(Binder)
    since 1.5 in favor of ServiceModuleExtender.addPeerSourceFactory(Class) and its' overloaded versions
    bt.module.ServiceModule.contributeTrackerFactory(Binder)
    since 1.5 in favor of ServiceModuleExtender.addTrackerFactory(Class, String, String...) and its' overloaded versions
    bt.net.IConnectionSource.getConnection(Peer, TorrentId)
    This is no longer used
    bt.torrent.TorrentRegistry.getDescriptor(Torrent)
    since 1.3 in favor of TorrentRegistry.getDescriptor(TorrentId)
    bt.data.DataDescriptor.getFilesForPiece(int)
    use DataDescriptor.getAllPiecesForFiles(Set) or DataDescriptor.getPiecesWithOnlyFiles(Set) instead
    bt.torrent.TorrentRegistry.getOrCreateDescriptor(Torrent, Storage)
    since 1.3 in favor of more clearly named TorrentRegistry.register(Torrent, Storage, FileDownloadCompleteCallback)
    bt.dht.DHTService.getPeers(Torrent)
    since 1.3 in favor of DHTService.getPeers(TorrentId)
    bt.peer.PeerSourceFactory.getPeerSource(Torrent)
    since 1.3 in favor of PeerSourceFactory.getPeerSource(TorrentId)
    bt.tracker.Tracker.request(Torrent)
    since 1.3 in favor of Tracker.request(TorrentId)
